%C5%A1n%C3%AD%20odborn%C3%A9%20terminologii%20jde%20o%20takzvan%C3%A9%20podkalibern%C3%AD,
- hlavn%C4%9B%20p%C5%99i%20v%C3%BDst%C5%99elu%20a%20ke%20stabilizaci%20st%C5%99ely.%20i -
